    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"71c1b41b-cb69-4cb4-880b-7d52fdaa5446\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>See <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661545\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrDisplace</a> for how to add scalar and vector displacement as well as displacement layers.</p></div></div><ul><li><p>Add a PxrDisplace VOP to your RIS Network and connect to the PxrMaterialBuilder's output_collect node.  Wire your displacement map such as creating a <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661707\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrTexture</a> VOP or <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661679\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrPtexture</a> VOP for texture or ptex respectively.  We can wire a shading network also.  We recommend vector-based displacement, especially when layering.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Wire your PxrDisplace VOP to the shader input of the output_collect node.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644642/rfh_connectDisplacement.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433131067&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644642/rfh_connectDisplacement.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433131067&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"480\" data-width=\"312\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644678\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_connectDisplacement.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644642\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"aa3c6ac1-170a-4895-b90a-33839ddcf239\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><ul><li><p>Displacement settings are found on the RenderMan tab &gt; Primvars &gt; Shading &gt; Displacement on the geometry OBJ being displaced. </p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center;\"> <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"325\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644642/displaceprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433130897&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=325&amp;height=269\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644642/displaceprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433130897&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644675\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"displaceprimvar.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644642\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5d23ae6c-ee24-4018-a508-6da44db19e0b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644642/displaceprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433130897&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=361&amp;height=299 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644642/displaceprimvar.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433130897&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=325&amp;height=269 1x\"></span></p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-tip conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"d59c4c45-64d5-4300-b342-04436260d8ae\" data-macro-name=\"tip\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-approve confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Trace displacements is on by default.</p><p>Set a displacement bound to render displacement, a setting of 0 turns off displacement on the object.</p></div></div><p /><p /><p />"
    }
